    .container
        .row
            .col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-lg-6
                h2.font-weight-light.text-light Second Language World
                p Our mission at Second Language World is to make it possible for ESL (English as a Second Language) Teachers looking for a job abroad to be as informed as possible. We also hope to bring a needed layer of transparency into ESL Schools.
                p
                    a.text-light-secondary(href='#')
                        i.mdi.mdi-map-marker(aria-hidden='true')
                        |  Based in Montreal, Canada 	
                p
                    a.text-light-secondary(href='#')
                        i.mdi.mdi-email(aria-hidden='true')
                        |  secondlanguageworld@gmail.com
                h1
                    a.text-light-secondary(href='#') 
                        i.mdi.mdi-facebook-box(aria-hidden='true')
                    a.text-light-secondary(href='#') 
                        i.mdi.mdi-twitter-box(aria-hidden='true')
                    a.text-light-secondary(href='#') 
